<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f4f6f9;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background: #f4f6f9;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5515f 0%, #9f041b 100%);
            padding: 40px 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .body {
            padding: 36px 40px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5515f 0%, #9f041b 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .expiry-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            color: #856404;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: #fff8f8;
            border: 1px solid #fdd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fc;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <span class="icon">üîê</span>
                <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
                <p>We received a request to reset your MarketX password.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="body">
                <p class="greeting">Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
                <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:1.7;">
                    Click the button below to reset your password. This link is valid for
                    <strong>{{expiryTime}}</strong>.
                </p>

                <div class="cta" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:12px;">
                    <span class="expiry-badge">‚è± Link expires in {{expiryTime}}</span>
                </div>

                <div class="cta">
                    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn">Reset My Password</a>
                </div>

                <p style="font-size:13px;color:#888;text-align:center;margin-top:12px;">
                    Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br />
                    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="color:#f5515f;word-break:break-all;">{{resetUrl}}</a>
                </p>

                <div class="warning-box">
                    <strong>üîí Security Notice:</strong><br />
                    If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email ‚Äî your password will remain
                    unchanged.
                    If you're concerned about your account security, please contact our support team immediately.
                </div>

                <p style="font-size:14px;color:#666;margin-top:24px;">Best regards,<br /><strong>The MarketX Security
                        Team</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>This is an automated security email from MarketX. Please do not reply.</p>
                <p>&copy; {{year}} MarketX Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>